---
title: Black Bean & Sweet Potato Tacos with Blistered Corn and Avocado-Lime Crema
description: This smoky-sweet taco filling can stand toe-to-toe with the best of them. Caramelized onion, sweet potato, and charred corn are tossed with honey, cumin, and lime for the flavor trifecta. A cool avocado-crema makes for the ultimate taco condiment.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-potato-and-black-bean-tacos-8b4567.jpg
